# AI Sales Visit Logger

A React Native (Expo) mobile application for field sales representatives to log customer visits and generate AI-assisted follow-up summaries.

This app allows users to record visit details, generate structured summaries using AI, store logs locally for offline use, and simulate syncing with a backend.

---

# Features

### Authentication

* User login and signup
* Session persistence using AsyncStorage

### Visit Logging

Users can create and edit visit logs including:

* Customer name
* Contact person
* Location
* Visit date
* Meeting notes
* Outcome status
* Next follow-up date

### AI Generated Summary

The app generates structured summaries from raw meeting notes including:

* Meeting summary
* Pain points
* Action items
* Recommended next steps

### Offline Support

* Visit logs are stored locally using AsyncStorage
* Users can create and edit visits without internet connection

### Sync System

Each visit log has a sync status:

* draft
* syncing
* synced
* failed

Failed sync attempts can be retried from the visit detail screen.

### Visit Detail Screen

* View full visit information
* View AI generated summary
* Retry sync if needed
* Edit visit entry

---

